  "texts": [
    "NPC300 and NPC650 were pooled 1:1 and loaded on a 1 channel and PHH on a 2 channel of the Single Cell A and B chips targeting 6000-8000 cells per each sample.",
    "All steps of the single-cell suspension preparation for the regenerating and embolized tissue samples were executed following the healthy tissue protocol.",
    "The next steps were conducted as described in the Chromium Single Cell 3' Reagent v2 and v3 Kits.",
    "In brief, after generation of the droplets with the single cells and barcoded beads, cDNA synthesis was performed.",
    "Next, droplets were broken, cDNA was amplified and libraries were constructed with different Chromium i7 Sample indexes in order to record sample assignment during computational analysis."
  ],
